title: Ready to Love MIA, Lizzo Interview, Houston Rockets, Wendy Williams and more.
itunes:title: Ready to Love MIA, Lizzo Interview, Houston Rockets, Wendy Williams and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride!  Whose word play is better?  Mr. Ready to Love is here in for The CLO to answer your love questions.  The ladies have a a little sumthin' sumthin' sweet just for you.  Three time Grammy winner Lizzo stopped by to talk about being Emmy nominated.  In NBA action,  Houston Rockets, WTF!?!?  Wendy Williams recently did an interview with The NY Post and went on a rant.  What would you do if your job paid you 300 times your salary?  This round of Would You Rather was about body parts and wrapped up the show with roles reversed and the ladies answering the questions.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
